    "description": "<p>Axisoft is a top-notch financial technology provider with offices in China (Hong Kong, Shanghai, Zhuhai, and Shenzhen) and Singapore. &nbsp;Since 1998, we have been helping global top-tier private banks improve their profitability through the deployment of our solutions in several countries and regions, such as China (including Hong Kong and Taiwan), Singapore, Australia, Japan, and Switzerland.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>In addition, we have been providing professional services of core banking systems to top-tier private banks in Asia. Our professional services help Financial Institutions implement, maintain and enhance their core banking systems. Throughout the years of experience in the core banking systems, we have established a professional team with solid experience and knowledge in core banking domain.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Following are the awards and certificates we received.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>• Hong Kong ICT Best FinTech Award</p>\n<p>• Hong Kong ICT Best Innovation &amp; Research Award</p>\n<p>• Asian Private Banker - Most Innovative Solution for the Technology Award</p>\n<p>• Asian Private Banker - Top Private Banking Technology Providers in Asia</p>\n<p>• China National Hi-Tech Enterprise&nbsp;</p>\n<p>• CMMI Level 3 Certificate</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>If you are a talented professional and desire the excitement of creating Financial Technology, software and solutions that will affect millions seriously, consider Axisoft as we are a place to make a difference. We offer competitive remuneration, comprehensive fringe benefits, international exposure, promising career prospect and opportunities to work in global top-tier financial institutions.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>For further information about Axisoft, visit www.axisoft.com.</p>",
